            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_1714564991837429670.png",
                "id": "talent40495",
                "key": "Tail Sweep ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Tail Sweep "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p>If this character has <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fontemer Pearl</span> attached, that <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> +1. (Once per Round)<br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\"><br>Fontemer Pearl</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached takes DMG:</span> Negate 1 DMG. Once per Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> will not be used when negating DMG from Summons.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p><p><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When you declare the end of your Round:</span> If the character to which this is attached is the active character, draw 1 card.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/4512ed5fa47440d951f659ff9f7fb0b3_5247298513895089778.png",
                "id": "talent25541",
                "key": "Swirling School of Fish",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Swirling School of Fish"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Elemental Burst</p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>, attaches <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fontemer Pearl</span> to this character, and summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Resonant Coral Orb</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Fontemer Pearl</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached takes DMG:</span> Negate 1 DMG. Once per Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> will not be used when negating DMG from Summons.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p><p><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When you declare the end of your Round:</span> If the character to which this is attached is the active character, draw 1 card.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/14274ea236c0c28ce99979f7fceb56a9_6464333450445571977.png",
                "id": "talent21378",
                "key": "Fontemer Hoarthunder",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Fontemer Hoarthunder"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When the battle begins, attach <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fontemer Pearl</span> to this character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Fontemer Pearl</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached takes DMG:</span> Negate 1 DMG. Once per Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> will not be used when negating DMG from Summons.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p><p><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When you declare the end of your Round:</span> If the character to which this is attached is the active character, draw 1 card.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/fa578f3705c431012e2d1447eda1f030_5266077439040247894.png",
                "id": "talent99883",
                "key": "Pearl Armor",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pearl Armor"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6433237158483596057.png",
                "id": "talent65874",
                "key": "Resonant Coral Orb",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/ee6e71485195ca50df31411b1c344717_7961415793003720561.png",
                "title": "Resonant Coral Orb"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_444219928440501114.png",
                "id": "talent6386",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_1657203598881240571.png",
